---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Container from "../../components/Container.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="World of Alphabets — Khonsu Development"
  description="Discover writing systems from around the world — flashcards, quizzes, maps, and tailored learning."
  canonicalPath="/alphabets"
>
  <section class="py-12 sm:py-16">
    <Container>
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <article
          class="prose prose-invert prose-headings:tracking-tight prose-p:text-zinc-200 prose-li:text-zinc-200 max-w-none"
        >
          <h1>Learn new alphabets easily</h1>
          <p>
            Discover <strong>World of Alphabets</strong> — a free mobile app designed
            to teach writing systems from all around the world.
          </p>

          <h2>Features</h2>

          <h3>Vast choice of scripts</h3>
          <p>
            Learn about <strong>267+ writing systems</strong>, and the signs for <strong
              >54</strong
            > of them. Discover constructed scripts and fictitious alphabets from
            the Lord of the Rings, Star Wars, and more.
          </p>

          <h3>Learn the story behind the alphabets</h3>
          <p>
            Discover each alphabet's history, characteristics and related
            languages. Each script is a fascinating world!
          </p>

          <h3>Alphabet overview</h3>
          <p>
            Get an instant overview of each alphabet: the letter, its name, its
            transliteration and its sound in a glance.
          </p>

          <h3>Flashcards</h3>
          <p>
            Use flashcards to learn each character at your own pace, including
            how to write it by hand, and how it's most often pronounced.
          </p>

          <h3>Script Map</h3>
          <p>
            Navigate a world of scripts. The birthplaces of all <strong
              >267+ scripts</strong
            > have been meticulously added to this map.
          </p>

          <h3>Languages</h3>
          <p>
            Learn about <strong>628+ languages</strong>, real and constructed,
            and which writing systems they use.
          </p>

          <h3>Dark mode</h3>
          <p>
            Experience sleek elegance and eye comfort with the dark theme —
            tailored for night-time or all-day use.
          </p>

          <h3>Tailored quiz</h3>
          <p>
            Challenge yourself to a multiple-choice quiz, to learn each sign.
            You can even design your own quizzes.
          </p>

          <h2>54 writing systems to discover</h2>
          <p>
            American Sign Language, Anatolian Hieroglyphs, Arabic, Aramaic,
            Armenian, Aurebesh, Baybayin, Braille, Cherokee, Coptic, Cuneiform,
            Cyrillic, Devanagari, Egyptian Hieroglyphs, Elder Futhark, Futhorc,
            Ge'ez, Georgian (Asomtavruli), Georgian (Mkhedruli), Georgian
            (Nuskhuri), Glagolitic, Gothic, Greek (Ancient), Greek (Modern),
            Hebrew, Hiragana, Inuktitut, Katakana, Khmer, Klingon, Korean
            (Hangul), Latin, Linear B, Lontara, Lycian, Lydian, Malayalam, Maya,
            Mongolian, Morse, N'Ko, Neo-Tifinagh, Ogham, Old Italic, Old Turkic
            (Orkhon), Phoenician, Semaphore, Syriac, Telugu, Tengwar, Thaana,
            Thai, Tibetan, Younger Futhark
          </p>

          <p>
            More alphabets will be integrated soon! Leave a comment on Google
            Play to let us know which alphabet or script you want to see added
            to the app.
          </p>

          <p>
            If you found a bug or a content error, please report it to{" "}
            <a href="mailto:khonsu.development@gmail.com"
              >khonsu.development@gmail.com</a
            >.
          </p>
        </article>

        <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row sm:items-center">
          <a
            class="btn btn-primary"
            href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=eu.khonsu.alphabets"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            target="_blank"
          >
            Get it on Google Play
          </a>
          <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/apps/world-of-alphabets">
            View on this site
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-10 text-sm text-zinc-400">
          <a
            class="underline decoration-white/20 underline-offset-4 hover:text-white"
            href="/alphabets/terms-and-conditions-for-world-of-alphabets"
          >
            Terms &amp; Conditions for World of Alphabets
          </a>
          {" · "}
          <a
            class="underline decoration-white/20 underline-offset-4 hover:text-white"
            href="/alphabets/privacy-policy-for-world-of-alphabets"
          >
            Privacy Policy for World of Alphabets
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
